### Combined Effect Testing
### ============================

### Low Temperature + High Helpfulness
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "User: What's the difference between TCP and UDP?\nAssistant:",
  "trait": "helpfulness",
  "scalar": 3.0,
  "max_tokens": 150,
  "temperature": 0.2,
  "top_p": 0.9,
  "repetition_penalty": 1.2
}

